00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,080
 kod sebe domo,

610
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:13,040
 to je drugo sad pitanje.

611
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:13,340
 Da.

612
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:16,760
 Da.

